#

Pan-Seared Salmon with Lemon Dill Butter Sauce and Garlic Roasted Asparagus

$25
450 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

FishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-ProteinLow-Carb

Tags:

SeafoodHealthyQuick Meal

Description

A succulent salmon fillet perfectly seared, topped with a zesty lemon dill butter sauce, paired with crisp garlic roasted asparagus for a refreshing and nutritious meal.

Ingredients

  • Salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • Butter: 1/4 cup
  • Lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Fresh dill: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
